    "body": "Using this [mono.yml](https://github.com/AppImage/pkg2appimage/blob/master/recipes/mono.yml) recipe, Mono 5.18.0.225 gets bundled. I don't have enough clue about Mono to make OpenRA work with it, though.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ ./Mono_Runtime-5.18.0.225.glibc2.15-x86_64.AppImage --version\r\nMono JIT compiler version 5.18.0.225 (tarball Fri Dec 21 19:41:01 UTC 2018)\r\nCopyright (C) 2002-2014 Novell, Inc, Xamarin Inc and Contributors. www.mono-project.com\r\n\tTLS:           __thread\r\n\tSIGSEGV:       altstack\r\n\tNotifications: epoll\r\n\tArchitecture:  amd64\r\n\tDisabled:      none\r\n\tMisc:          softdebug \r\n\tInterpreter:   yes\r\n\tLLVM:          yes(600)\r\n\tSuspend:       preemptive\r\n\tGC:            sgen (concurrent by default)\r\n```"
