    "body": "This is something i've been thinking about for a while, but only recently started filing issues about.\r\n\r\nMy current plan, hopefully for Next + 1:\r\n* [Remove the dependency on System.Drawing and libgdiplus](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/15955)\r\n* Package the `mono-5.10.0-debian-7-x64` runtime from https://download.mono-project.com/runtimes/raw/ (the last version that Microsoft provide debian 7 builds for)\r\n* Resurrect our old [recursive library detection script](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/blob/4c8575b1f53d5bff8b2e92e905dfe2f982f8c9f3/packaging/osx/package.sh) to identify the managed libraries we need to ship\r\n\r\nI suspect that we will then switch to .NET core after #15954 is complete. "
